                      lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#19v #28r #34r #90v #101v" facs="022 030 036 093 104"/>, etc.);
                      lines of text are written in the upper margin with a symbol (+) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#15r #41v #101v" facs="017 044 104"/>);
                      erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#11v #21r #44v #49v #50v" facs="014 023 047 052 053"/>, etc.);
                      text has been removed (<locus target="#5r #6r #7v #12r #14v" facs="007 008 010 014 017"/>, etc.)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
